6) How to review this MR efficiently

 1. Read Behavior-preserving levers first (sets intent and safety model).
 2. Review the 6 behavioral-risk files line-by-line.
 3. Validate the manual mapper closure table (answers “what about non-web mappers?”).
 4. Spot-check safety net on representative contracts (CODE/AOC/Agreements + BigDecimal).
 5. End with the 3 conscious acceptances (IT gate, pre-existing @SecureWithTokens, test-only nature).

